OL,6,FWatch as Amy Pugh calls 999 and
OL,7,Fpretends her husband had taken his own
OL,8,Flife
OL,10,FA woman who staged her husband's death
OL,11,Fto emergency services has been
OL,12,Fsentenced to 13 years in prison at
OL,13,FStafford Crown Court.
OL,15,FAmy Pugh, 34 of Stafford Road in
OL,16,FWolverhampton was found guilty of
OL,17,Fmurdering her estranged husband, 32-
OL,18,Fyear-old Kyle Pugh in June 2025.
