OL,6,FEarlier in the trial, the court heard
OL,7,Fhow Pugh and Kyle, had an argument at
OL,8,Fher then home on Aston Drive, Newport
OL,9,Fin March 2022.
OL,11,FMr Pugh was in a new relationship with
OL,12,Fanother woman at the time of the
OL,13,Fattack, but was visiting his children
OL,14,Fat the family home that he had shared
OL,15,Fwith the defendant.
OL,17,FThe argument led to an altercation
OL,18,Fbetween the two, where Pugh has
OL,19,Finjured Kyle causing him to become
OL,20,Funresponsive.
