OL,6,FAddressing Pugh, who wore a pink top
OL,7,Fand a black blazer in the dock, the
OL,8,Fjudge said: "Kyle Pugh was a cherished
OL,9,Fson and brother and a conscientious
OL,10,Ffather. He is mourned by his family
OL,11,Fwho have had to try and come to terms
OL,12,Fwith his death in the context of your
OL,13,Fcallous deception of how it happened.
OL,15,F"Your relationship was described by
OL,16,Feveryone, including yourself, as
OL,17,Ftoxic. There was a volatile dynamic
OL,18,Fbetween you and him which escalated
OL,19,Fover time.
