OL,6,F"As your relationship deteriorated,
OL,7,Fthe boundaries between victim and
OL,8,Faggressor blurred. I accept that
OL,9,Fviolence was introduced into your
OL,10,Frelationship by Kyle Pugh, but there
OL,11,Fcame a point where you began to employ
OL,12,Fverbal and physical retaliation."
OL,14,F'I've been sat here playing music
OL,15,Fdrinking'
OL,17,FAfter the incident, Amy Pugh took 20
OL,18,Fminutes to call emergency services.
OL,19,FDuring this time the court was told
OL,20,Fhow she made several phone calls to
OL,21,Fher father before calling 999.
