OL,6,FWhen emergency services arrived at the
OL,7,Fscene at around 9.15pm, Pugh was
OL,8,Fcarrying out CPR on an unresponsive
OL,9,FKyle.
OL,11,FAmy acted distressed when police and
OL,12,Fparamedics arrived asking, "Has he got
OL,13,Fa pulse or what? because there's a
OL,14,Fchance that he will survive this
OL,15,Fstupidity".
OL,17,FShe also said "I've saved him so many
OL,18,Ftimes".
