OL,6,FKyle was then taken to the Princess
OL,7,FRoyal Hospital where he sadly died the
OL,8,Ffollowing day.
OL,10,FThe trial was told the couple had had
OL,11,Fa "volatile, turbulent and abusive"
OL,12,Frelationship and they had separated at
OL,13,Fthe time of the alleged attack.
OL,15,FDuring the investigation officers
OL,16,Fdiscovered that Kyle had sent messages
OL,17,Fto family and friends throughout the
OL,18,Fday of the incident making plans with
OL,19,Fthem, including a voice note sent to a
OL,20,Ffriend about seeing them later that
OL,21,Fnight.
