OL,6,FThe court also heard how Pugh took a
OL,7,Fphone call from Kyle's girlfriend on
OL,8,Fhis phone at around 9pm. Kyle's phone
OL,9,Fhas never been recovered.
OL,11,FA postmortem carried out on Kyle's
OL,12,Fbody showed that he had suffered neck
OL,13,Fcompression injuries.
OL,15,FPugh cried in the dock and was handed
OL,16,Fa tissue by a dock officer as Sam
OL,17,FRobinson KC, defending, detailed
OL,18,Fprevious incidents of violence she had
OL,19,Fsuffered at the hands of Mr Pugh.
