OL,7,Fnature of the relationship that
OL,8,Fexisted between them.
OL,10,F"This is a case of impaired judgment
OL,11,Fand a lack of self-control, but not
OL,12,Fone of malice.
OL,14,F"During the course of a fast-moving
OL,15,Fconfrontation, this was not a planned
