OL,6,FIn her sentencing remarks, the judge
OL,7,Fsaid: "You had struck Kyle Pugh with
OL,8,Fsuch force that his nose and eye
OL,9,Fsocket had been broken and then you
OL,10,Fcompressed his neck by using either a
OL,11,Fchokehold or a forearm against his
OL,12,Fwindpipe.
OL,14,F"Such force was deployed that when you
OL,15,Frestricted the blood flow to his brain
OL,16,Fand he slipped into unconsciousness,
OL,17,Fyour reaction was to call your father.
